									<article itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/NewsArticle" id="post-767632" class="post-767632 post post-excerpt hentry track_event"  data-event-tracking="Outfit| 0| Primary – 13 Text 1 Large 6 Small| 0| 1| zon| HP top stories&quot; " >
										<header>	
						<h2 itemprop="name" class="entry-title"><a itemprop="url" href="http://montrealgazette.com/news/world/nancy-and-ronald-reagan-inseparable-in-life-together-again" target="_self" rel="bookmark" title="">Friends, family say final farewells to Nancy Reagan</a></h2>					</header>

										<div itemprop="articleBody" class="entry-content">
						Close friends and family remembered Nancy Reagan as more than a first lady Friday, recalling at her funeral service how she and husband Ronald Reagan made up “two halves of ...					</div>
										
