										<header>	
						<h3 itemprop="name" class="entry-title"><a itemprop="url" href="http://driving.ca/nissan/leaf/auto-news/news/self-driving-cars-will-worsen-traffic-and-nobody-will-care/" target="_blank" rel="bookmark" title="">Self-driving cars will increase traffic – and nobody will care</a></h3>					</header>

										
					<figure class="thumbnail " ><a id="link-0" href="http://driving.ca/nissan/leaf/auto-news/news/self-driving-cars-will-worsen-traffic-and-nobody-will-care/" target="_blank"><img itemprop="image" src="http://i2.wp.com/wpmedia.driving.ca/2014/12/stockvolvoautodriving7.jpg?resize=410,307&#038;quality=55&#038;strip=all" 
				class="attachment-post-thumbnail wp-post-image " 
